x4freetext: The helions and tritons were detected by
means of silicon semiconductor counters. In helion case
a telescope with delta-E 70-300 mum and E 2-3 mm was
employed. For tritons two choices were made,
one delta-E 400-150 mum and E 3-2 mm, corresponding to
the helion energies 22 MeV and 40 MeV and other
delta-E 400mum-1.4 mm and E approx. 3 mm, corresponding
For N-14, melamine C3N6H6 target, thickness approx.
Table data was received from Dr.A.S.Demyanova
